### Create role
POST http://localhost:3000/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "BARTENDER"
}

### Get all roles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/roles

### Update role
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/roles/{2}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MANAGER"
}

### Delete role by id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/roles/{2}

